	  <li><a href=3D"https://hefferon.net/other/">Other stuff from me</a>,
	      including programs and documents.</li>
	  <li><a href=3D"https://hefferon.net/jimhefferon.html">About me</a>.
	      </li>
	  <li><a href=3D"https://hefferon.net/">This site's home page</a>.
	      </li>
	</ul>=09
